{"tid":2439144,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"黃大仙25歲男衰咸濕Tinder墮裸聊陷阱 遭勒索1萬元點數卡","createTime":"2021-03-09T04:43:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T11:17:53.000Z","uid":44209,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ca9ff746fe695023a28a80bc360a5a86bca0d88e","tid":2439144,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T04:43:57.000Z","msg":"黃大仙25歲男墮裸聊陷阱 遭勒索1萬元點數卡<br />\n<br />\n2021-03-09 08:44<br />\n<br />\n黃大仙聯合道一名25歲男子早前疑在交友軟件被拍下不雅影片，遭勒索共約值一萬元的點數卡，昨晚報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n警方昨日傍晚11時13分接獲該名姓蘇的青年報案，指早前於交友軟件Tinder懷疑被一名女子拍下裸聊影片，對方其後聯同另一名男子，要求事主購買共值約一萬港元的點數卡。<br />\n<br />\n警方接報到場，經初步調查，將案件列勒索，並交由黃大仙警區刑事調查隊第三隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。"},{"pid":"ddab6e509bb71178401624af0be7ba910da6bcf4","tid":2439144,"uid":44209,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T04:44:45.000Z","msg":"17歲仔玩匿名交友app「Heymandi」裸聊 遭勒索2千元<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2321646\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2321646</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"65029f7683c1bcdb43b4c487f6240b6a93601413","tid":2439144,"uid":224533,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T04:46:38.000Z","msg":"男人咪由鳩佢貼囉 邊撚個睇<br />\n畀人勒索報狗仲柒"},{"pid":"3d22909b3b06b9ebd7afbfe1cdeb924ce8b3214c","tid":2439144,"uid":58630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T04:46:43.000Z","msg":"點解仲有人會咁撚蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2bc384448c7cf4cec51b7ade300bd6fbff013aa","tid":2439144,"uid":118647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T04:47:00.000Z","msg":"笑𠹌咗"},{"pid":"b9dc31f65cff65846bb1a8963f9d3d93a1936839","tid":2439144,"uid":49276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T04:47:46.000Z","msg":"衰弱智就真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e2c0306b830fccd15f085dbc6c636622bd41dd1","tid":2439144,"uid":123696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65029f7683c1bcdb43b4c487f6240b6a936